#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Help System Handbook"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help System"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The help system is designed to make accessing the common &UNIX; help systems "
"(<application>man</application> and <application>info</application>) simple, "
"as well as the user documentation of applications including &plasma-"
"workspaces; from the &kde; community (&XML;)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All applications (including &plasma-workspaces;) from the &kde; community "
"come fully documented, thanks to the efforts of the Documentation team. If "
"you are interested in helping with the documentation efforts, join the "
"<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">mailing "
"list</ulink> and write to the team at <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</"
"email>. No experience is required, just enthusiasm and patience."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to help translating &kde; documentation to your native "
"language, review the information, including coordinators for each language "
"team, on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">Localization web site</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invoking Help"
msgstr "Tilkalle hjelp"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "&khelpcenter; can be called in several ways:"
msgstr "&khelpcenter; kan startes på flere måter:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu"
msgstr "Fra <guimenu>Hjelp</guimenu>- menyen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common will probably be from within an application. Choose "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Application</replaceable> Handbook</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to open that application's handbook."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the Application Launcher"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the big <guiicon>K</guiicon> in your panel, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem> from the <guimenuitem>Applications</"
"guimenuitem> tab or type <userinput>help</userinput> followed by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem>. This will open &khelpcenter; with the "
"default start page."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the command line"
msgstr "Fra kommandolinja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; may be started using a &URL; to display a file. &URL;s have "
"been added for <command>info</command> and <command>man</command> pages "
"also. You can use them as follows:"
msgstr ""
"&khelpcenter; kan startes med en &URL; for å vise en fil. &URL;-er er også "
"lagt til for <command>info</command> og <command>man</command>-sider. Du kan "
"bruke dem slik:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application help file"
msgstr "En programhjelpefil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the &kwrite; help file, at the contents page."
msgstr "Åpner hjelpefila for &kwrite; på innholdssida."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "A local &URL;"
msgstr "En lokal &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Man page"
msgstr "En man-side"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "An Info page"
msgstr "En  info-side"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invoking <command>khelpcenter</command> with no parameters opens the default "
"start page."
msgstr ""
"Om kommandoen <command>khelpcenter</command> gis uten argumenter åpnes "
"standard startside."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface"
msgstr "&khelpcenter;-brukerflaten"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface consists of two panes of information."
msgstr "Brukerflaten til &khelpcenter; består av to informasjonsruter."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar and menus are explained further in <xref linkend=\"menu-and-"
"toolbar-ref\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Verktøylinja og menyene forklares videre i <xref linkend=\"menu-and-toolbar-"
"ref\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Documents contain their own navigation tools, enabling you to move either "
"sequentially through a document, using <guilabel>Next</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Previous</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> links, or "
"to move around in a less structured manner, using hyperlinks."
msgstr ""
"Diokumenter inneholder sine egne navigeringsverktøy, som du kan bruke til "
"enten å gå sekvensielt gjennom dokumentet med knappene <guilabel>Neste</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Forrige</guilabel> og <guilabel>Innhold</guilabel>, "
"eller flytte rundt på en mindre strukturert måte ved bruk av hyperlenker."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Links can take you to other parts of the same document, or to a different "
"document, and you can use the <guiicon>Back</guiicon> (Left pointing arrow) "
"or <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> (Right pointing arrow) icons on the toolbar to "
"move through the documents you have viewed in this session."
msgstr ""
"Lenker kan føre til andre deler av det samme dokumentet, eller til et annet "
"dokument, og du kan bruke ikonene <guiicon>Tilbake</guiicon> (pil til "
"venstre) og <guiicon>Fram</guiicon> (pil til høyre) på verktøylinja til å gå "
"gjennom de dokumentene du har sett på i denne økta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two panes display the contents of the help system, and the help files "
"themselves, on the left and right respectively."
msgstr ""
"De to rutene viser innholdet i hjelpesystemet, og selve hjelpefilene, "
"henholdsvis til venstre og høyre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Pane"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane in &khelpcenter; is displayed on the left hand side of the "
"window. As you might expect, you can move the splitter bar, to make sure you "
"can comfortably read the contents of either pane."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane is further divided into three tabs, one containing a <link "
"linkend=\"contents-tab\">tree view</link> showing all the help information "
"&khelpcenter; is aware of, and the other contains the &kde; <link linkend="
"\"kde-glossary\">glossary</link> of terms. On the third tab you can "
"configure the <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Innhold-fanen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab contains the following default top "
"level entries in the tree view:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fundamentals"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Fundamentals introduce you to the many features of the &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications; and describe many common tasks you can "
"perform in all &applications;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma Manual"
msgstr "Plasma-håndbok"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &plasma; Manual is the documentation for the &plasma-workspaces;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Hjelp på nettverket"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A page with links to online help and additional information provided by the "
"&kde; community."
msgstr ""
"En side med lenker til hjelp på nettverket og mer informasjon levert av "
"&kde;-fellesskapet."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Manuals"
msgstr "Programhåndbøker"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Native &kde; application documentation. All &kde; applications have "
"documentation in &XML; format, which are converted to <acronym>HTML</"
"acronym> when you view them. This section lists all the &kde; applications "
"with a brief description and a link to the full application documentation."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentasjon for programmer som tilhører &kde;. Alle &kde;-programmer har "
"dokumentasjon i &XML;-format, som gjøres om til <acronym>HTML</acronym> når "
"du ser på dem. Dette avsnittet lister opp alle &kde;-programmene med en kort "
"beskrivelse og en lenke til hele programdokumentasjonen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The applications are displayed in a tree structure that echoes the default "
"structure of the <guimenu>K</guimenu> menu, making it easy to find the "
"application you are looking for."
msgstr ""
"Programmet vises i en trestruktur som ligger nær standardstrukturen i "
"<guimenu>K</guimenu>-menyen, så det blir lett å finne programmet du ser "
"etter."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Settings Modules</guilabel> entities"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provide a list of links to various modules in the &systemsettings; "
"application or to modules for &konqueror;, Filemanager or Browser."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "KInfoCenter Modules"
msgstr "KinfoCenter-modulene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains a list of links to various KInfocenter modules documentation."
msgstr ""
"Inneholder en liste over lenker til dokumentasjon for de ymse modulene i "
"KinfoCenter."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "KIO Workers"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contains a list of links to various <acronym>KIO</acronym> modules "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Inneholder en liste over lenker til dokumentasjon for en rekke <acronym>KIO</"
"acronym>-moduler."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "&UNIX; manual pages"
msgstr "&UNIX; manualsider"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UNIX; man pages are the traditional on-line documentation format for &UNIX; "
"systems. Most programs on your system will have a man page. In addition, man "
"pages exist for programming functions and file formats."
msgstr ""
"&UNIX; man-sider er det tradisjonelle formatet for datalagret dokumentasjon "
"for &UNIX;-systemer. De fleste programmer på systemet har en man-side. "
"Dessuten finnes det man-sider for funksjoner brukt i programmering, og for "
"filformater."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollkeeper"
msgstr "Scrollkeeper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional non-&kde; documentation installed on your system."
msgstr "Ekstra dokumentasjon utenom &kde; som er installert på systemet."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Info Pages"
msgstr "Les info-sider"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"TeXinfo documentation is used by many &GNU; applications, including "
"<command>gcc</command> (the C/C++ compiler), <command>emacs</command>, and "
"many others."
msgstr ""
"TeXinfo-dokumentasjon brukes av mange &GNU;-programmer, bl.a. <command>gcc</"
"command> (C/C++-kompilatoren), <command>emacs</command>, og mange andre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel> tab"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching the help files is fairly intuitive, enter the word(s) you wish to "
"search for in the text box, choose your options (if any), and press "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton>. The results display in the viewer pane to the "
"right."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search is not case sensitive, &ie; uppercase and lowercase characters are "
"considered the same. For example, if you search for <quote>Shortcut</quote>, "
"results that contain <quote>shortcut</quote> will be returned as well."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "The options available are:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Method"
msgstr "Metode"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose how to search for multiple words. If you choose <guilabel>and</"
"guilabel>, results are returned only if all your search terms are included "
"in the page. <guilabel>or</guilabel> returns results if <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> of the search terms are found."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your searches are not returning the results you expect, check carefully "
"you haven't excluded the wrong search term with an erroneous setting."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max. results"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Determines the maximum number of results returned from your search."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scope selection"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to select the sections where the search will be done. The "
"available options quickly select the most common option, while "
"<guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem> allows one to select single sections."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>Man</application> and <application>Info</application> "
"sections"
msgstr ""
"<application>Man</application> og <application>info</application>-avsnittene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man pages are the standard &UNIX; manual pages, and have been in use for "
"many years on many operating systems. They are extremely thorough, and are "
"the very best place to get information about most &UNIX; commands and "
"applications. When people say <quote>RTFM</quote>, the Manual they are "
"referring to is very often the man page."
msgstr ""
"Man-sider er standard &UNIX; manualsider og har vært i bruk i mange år på "
"mange operativsystemer. De er svært grundige og er det beste stedet å finne "
"informasjon om de fleste &UNIX;-kommandoer og programmer. Når noen sier "
"<quote>RTFM</quote> er den Manualen de henviser til svært ofte man-sida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The man pages are not perfect. They tend to be in depth, but also extremely "
"technical, often written by developers, and for developers. In some cases "
"this makes them somewhat unfriendly, if not downright impossible for many "
"users to understand. They are, however, the best source of solid information "
"on most command line applications, and very often the only source."
msgstr ""
"Man-sidene er ikke fullkomne. De går gjerne i dybden, men er også svært "
"tekniske, ofte skrevet av utviklere for utviklere. I noen tilfeller blir de "
"derfor uvennlige, om ikke rett og slett ubegripelige for mange brukere. De "
"er likevel den beste kilden til solid informasjon om de fleste kommandolinje-"
"programmene, og svært ofte den eneste kilden."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you've ever wondered what the number is when people write things like "
"man(1) it means which section of the manual the item is in. You will see "
"&khelpcenter; uses the numbers to divide the very many man pages into their "
"own sections, making it easier for you to find the information you're "
"looking for, if you're just browsing."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du noen gang har lurt på hva tallet betyr når noen skriver slikt som "
"man(1), så betyr det hvilken del av manualen sida hører til. Du vil se at "
"&khelpcenter; bruker tallene til å dele opp det store antallet man-sider i "
"egne avsnitt. Dette gjør det lettere for deg å finne informasjonen du er ute "
"etter, hvis du bare blar omkring."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also available are the Info pages, intended to be a replacement for the man "
"pages. The maintainer of some applications no longer update the man pages, "
"so if there is both a man page and an info page available, the info page is "
"probably the most recent. Most applications have one or the other though. If "
"the application you are looking for help on is a &GNU; utility, you will "
"most likely find it has an info page, not a man page."
msgstr ""
"Info-sidene finnes også, de er ment å bli en erstatning for man-sider. Noen "
"utviklere vedlikeholder ikke man-sidene lenger, så hvis det finnes både en "
"man-side og en info-side tilgjengelig er antakelig info-sida den nyeste. De "
"fleste programmer har enten den ene eller den andre. Hvis programmet du "
"søker hjelp med er et &GNU;-program har det høyst sannsynlig en info-side, "
"og ikke (en oppdatert) man-side."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating inside the <application>Info</application> pages"
msgstr "Navigering inne i <application>info</application>-sidene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info documents are arranged hierarchically with each page called a node. All "
"info documents have a <guilabel>Top</guilabel> node, &ie; the opening page. "
"You can return to the <guilabel>Top</guilabel> of an info document by "
"pressing <guilabel>Top</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Info-dokumenter arrangeres hierarkisk der hver side kalles en node. Alle "
"info-dokumenter har en <guilabel>Topp</guilabel>-node, dvs. åpningssida. Du "
"kan komme tilbake til <guilabel>Toppen</guilabel> av en info-side ved å "
"trykke <guilabel>Top</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Prev</guibutton> &amp; <guibutton>Next</guibutton> are used to "
"move to the previous/next page at the current level of the hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Forrige</guibutton> of <guibutton>Neste</guibutton> brukes til å "
"flytte mellom forrige/neste side på dette nivået av hierarkiet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a menu item within a document moves you to a lower level in the "
"hierarchy. You may move up the hierarchy by pressing <guibutton>Up</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Om du trykker på et meny-element inne i et dokument flyttes du til et lavere "
"nivå i hierarkiet. Du kan gå oppover et nivå ved å trykke <guibutton>Opp</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man is treated similarly to info, with the section index being the Top node "
"and each man page on the level below. Man entries are one page long."
msgstr ""
"Man behandles på liknende måte som info, der avsnittsregisteret er topp-"
"noden og hver man-side på nivået under. Man-filer er en  «side» lange."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kde; glossary"
msgstr "&kde;-ordlista"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The glossary provides a quick reference point, where you can look up the "
"definitions of words that may be unfamiliar to you. These range from &kde; "
"specific applications and technologies, through to general &UNIX; computing "
"terms."
msgstr ""
"Ordlista er et oppslagssted der du kan finne definisjon på ord du kanskje "
"ikke har sett før. Disse kan være fra programmer og teknologier som er "
"spesielle for &kde; til generell &UNIX;-terminologi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the left hand pane you will see a tree view, with two choices: "
"<guilabel>Alphabetically</guilabel> or <guilabel>By Topic</guilabel>. Both "
"contain the same entries, sorted differently, to allow you to quickly find "
"the item of interest."
msgstr ""
"På venstre side ser du en trevisning med to valg. <guilabel>Etter emne</"
"guilabel> og <guilabel>Alfabetisk</guilabel>. Begge listene inneholder det "
"samme, men sortert forskjellig slik at det skal være raskt å finne fram til "
"det som er av interesse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate down the tree views to the left, and items you select will be "
"displayed on the right."
msgstr ""
"Naviger nedover trevisningene til venstre, så vises forklaringen til høyre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus and toolbar"
msgstr "Menyer og verktøylinjer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; has a very minimal interface, allowing you to concentrate on "
"getting help rather than learning how to use the help browser."
msgstr ""
"&khelpcenter; har en sværtminimal brukerflate, så du kan konsentrere deg om "
"å finne hjelp i stedet for å lære å bruke hjelpesystemet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "The icons available to you in the toolbar are as follows:"
msgstr "Ikonene du kan bruke i verktøylinja er:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar Icons"
msgstr "Verktøylinje-ikoner"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "Innholdsfortegnelse"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490 index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the main start page of &khelpcenter;."
msgstr "Gå til startsida til &khelpcenter;."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Tilbake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous page you viewed. Click the check mark right to the icon. "
"This displays a list of previously viewed pages. Selecting one will take you "
"directly back to that page."
msgstr ""
"Gå til forrige side du så på. Trykk på V-merket til høyre for ikonet. Dette "
"viser en liste over tidligere sette sider. Velg en av dem for å gå direkte "
"tilbake til den sida."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Fram"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go forward one page. This icon is only active if you have already used the "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Gå framover én side. Dette ikonet er bare aktivt hvis du allerede har brukt "
"<guiicon>Tilbake</guiicon>-ikonet."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopier"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy text to the clipboard to be pasted in another application."
msgstr ""
"Kopier tekst til utklippstavla så den kan limes inn i et annet program."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Finn"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find a word or words within the currently visible page."
msgstr "Finn et eller flere ord i den sida som vises nå."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase Font Sizes"
msgstr "Øk skriftstørrelser"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase the size of the text in the viewer pane."
msgstr "Øk størrelsen på teksten i visningsruta."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrease Font Sizes"
msgstr "Minsk skriftstørrelser"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decrease the size of the text in the viewer pane. This icon is only enabled "
"if you have previously enlarged the text."
msgstr ""
"Minsk størrelsen på teksten i visningsruta. Dette ikonet er bare aktivt hvis "
"du har forstørret teksten tidligere."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus contain the following entries:"
msgstr "Menyene inneholder disse oppføringene:"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "File"
msgstr "Fil"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print the contents of the currently visible page. Handbooks in <acronym>PDF</"
"acronym> format you find on the <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/index.php?"
"language=en\"> &kde; Documentation Server</ulink>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Fil</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Avslutt</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close and exit &khelpcenter;"
msgstr "Lukk og avslutt &khelpcenter;"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Rediger"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Rediger</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopier</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy the selected text to the clipboard."
msgstr "Kopier den markerte teksten til utklippstavla."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Rediger</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Velg alt</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select all the text in the current page."
msgstr "Marker all teksten på gjeldende side."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Rediger</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Finn …</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find a word or words in the currently visible page."
msgstr "Finn et eller flere ord i den sida som vises nå."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Vis"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Set Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vis</guimenu><guisubmenu>Velg tegnkoding</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the encoding of the current page. Normally, the default setting of "
"<guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem> should be sufficient, but if you are "
"having problems viewing pages written in languages other than English, you "
"may need to choose a specific encoding in this menu."
msgstr ""
"Endre tegnkoding for gjeldende side. Som regel vil standardinnstillingen "
"<guimenuitem>Standard</guimenuitem> være nok, men hvis du har vansker med å "
"lese sider som er skrevet i andre språk enn engelsk kan det være du må velge "
"en bestemt tegnkoding i denne menyen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:690
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Set Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Full Screen Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vis</guimenu><guisubmenu>Velg tegnkoding</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes &khelpcenter; to full screen mode, in which the &khelpcenter; window "
"takes up the whole screen, and does not have the usual window decorations. "
"To exit full screen mode, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; "
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Gå</guimenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Table of Contents</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut><guimenu>Gå til</guimenu><guimenuitem>Innholdsfortegnelse</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgUp</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Page</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgUp</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Gå</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forrige side</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous page of the current documentation."
msgstr "Gå til forrige side av gjeldende dokumentasjon."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Page</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Gå</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Neste side</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next page of the current documentation."
msgstr "Gå til neste side av gjeldende dokumentasjon."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Left</keysym></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Venstre</keysym></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Gå</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tilbake</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go back to the previous page you were viewing."
msgstr "Gå til den forrige sida du så på."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Right</keysym></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Høyre</keysym></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Gå</guimenu><guimenuitem>Fram</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have previously moved back with the back icon or menu entry, you can "
"work your way forward again with this menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du tidligere har gått tilbake med bakover-ikonet eller menyoppføringen, "
"så kan du gå forover igjen med denne menyoppføringen."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Bokmerker"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a bookmark for the current page, the title of the pages is appended to "
"the bookmarks menu. Use the action <guimenuitem>Delete Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem> in the context menu of an item to remove it from the menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Bookmarks Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <guilabel>New Folder</guilabel> dialog where you can add new "
"submenuitems to the bookmarks menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Innstillinger"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Fonts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Innstillinger</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tilpass skrifter …</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to configure the font family and size used by &khelpcenter;."
msgstr ""
"Brukes til å sette opp skriftfamilie og størrelser brukt i &khelpcenter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &khelpcenter; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""

